# AMCP Clients

> Web and desktop client applications for the AI Modular Cybersecurity Platform.

## What lives here

This repository contains the user-facing applications and client-side presentation layer.

Includes:
- web UI
- desktop client
- shared client-side assets if needed
- front-end build and deployment configuration

## Repository layout

```text
amcp-clients/
├── interfaces/
└── README.md
```

## How to use it

1. Keep all user-facing applications here.
2. Talk only to stable APIs, SDKs, or events.
3. Do not depend on internal service or training code.

